<h2><img src="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/images/wrd.gif" align=left hspace=0 width=100 height=100>Game Management Home Page</h2>
<p>The Game Management Section is responsible for wisely managing Georgia&#146;s game animals. The Section also 
provides support and assistance with a variety of wildlife issues, including management, conservation and 
nuisance wildlife problems. The section also offers a variety of opportunities for wildlife-related recreation, 
including hunting and wildlife-viewing, on more than 1 million acres of wildlife management areas.</p>
<hr>
<p>Todd Holbrook, Chief<br>
DNR -- Wildlife Resources Division<br>
Game Management Section Click Here to read a message from the chief<br>
