        <p align="center"><em>7 Martin Luther King, Jr. Drive,
        Suite 450, Atlanta, GA 30334-9004</em> </p>
    </dd>
    <dd>
        <p align="center"><em>phone: (404) 651-5120 / toll free:
        1-800-685-2443 / fax: (404) 651-5130 / email: </em><a
        href="mailto:p2ad@ix.netcom.com"><em>p2ad@ix.netcom.com</em></a> </p>
    </dd>
    <div align="center"><center>
    <dt><img src="Elegant_Double.gif" width="536" height="5"></dt>
    </center></div>
