<h3><a name="P2">Pollution Prevention Sites</a></h3>
<h4>General</h4>
<p><a href="http://es.inel.gov/">Envirosense Homepage</a>
(http://es.inel.gov) This site attempts to provide a single
repository for P<sup>2</sup> and compliance assurance/
enforcement information and databases. Included are P<sup>2</sup>
case studies, technologies, points of contact, environmental
statutes, regulations, and much more.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.deq.state.mi.us/ead/">Michigan's</a>
pollution prevention site (http://www.deq.state.mi.us/ead)</p>
