(http://www.epa.gov/docs/enviro/html/ef_home.html) This is a
relational database integrating EPA's information holdings
including TRI, RCRA, and facility locator data.</p>
<p><a
href="http://es.inel.gov/program/p2dept/energy/epic/epic.html">DOE's
Pollution Prevention Information Exchange Clearinghouse</a>
(http://es.inel.gov/program/p2dept/energy/epic/epic.html) This
site has information on federal laws, regulations, policy,
guidance and other topics.</p>
<p><strong>Technical Assistance</strong></p>
<p>Find your local pollution prevention assistance agency through
the <a
