<h1 align="center"><a name="p2ad"><img
src="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/images/p2ad.gif"
align="absmiddle" width="100" height="100"><font color="#008000">Pollution
Prevention Assistance Division</font></a><font color="#004000"> </font></h1>
<p align="center">P<sup>2</sup>AD is your ONE-STOP SERVICE in
Georgia to reduce, reuse, and recycle waste and lower demand for
raw materials, water and energy. P<sup>2</sup>AD is a
non-regulatory state agency that offers technical assistance at
no cost to businesses, manufacturers, industries, the
agricultural sector, and government.</p>
