<h2 align="center"><b><blink>FREE SOFTWARE!!</blink></b></h2>
<p align="center">[<em>From the Source - </em>Fall 1995]</p>
<hr>
<p>P<sup>2</sup>AD is pleased to announce the availability of
&quot;Your Electronic Guide to Pollution Prevention&quot;. This
new software is designed to be an introduction to pollution
prevention in Georgia. The program has different modules to help
you understand what pollution prevention is, to explain how to
establish a pollution prevention program at your business, and to
detail the various services provided by P<sup>2</sup>AD. The
program is self-contained and runs in a Windows PC environment.
Instructions for installation and use are on the disk label. This
software is FREE, and available in 3.5&quot; HD floppy disk only.</p>
<p>You can obtain this software by: 1) calling us at (404)
651-5120 or 1-800-685-2443 and leaving your name and mailing
address with the secretary; 2) sending us an e-mail note
containing your mailing address to <a
href="mailto:p2ad@ix.netcom.com">p2ad@ix.netcom.com</a>.</p>
