<h2 align="center">An Analysis of Pollution Prevention
Opportunities and Impediments in the Wood Products Manufacturing
Sector in Georgia </h2>
<p align="center"><strong>April 1, 1996 </strong></p>
<p align="center"><strong>Prepared by </strong></p>
<p align="center"><strong>Paul Crumpler, Pollution Prevention
Engineer</strong> </p>
