<h3 align="center"><strong>GEORGIA DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL
RESOURCES</strong> </h3>
<h3 align="center"><strong>ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION DIVISION</strong> <br
wp="br1">
<br wp="br2">
</h3>
<h3 align="center"><strong>CHAPTER 391-3-11</strong> </h3>
<h3 align="center"><strong>HAZARDOUS WASTE MANAGEMENT</strong> <br
wp="br1">
</h3>
